02:06.032 --> 02:10.079
That's how ignorant they are, how biblically illiterate they are.

02:10.099 --> 02:12.183
So how do you bring the gospel to a place like this?

02:13.545 --> 02:14.226
We're gonna see

02:14.402 --> 02:26.739
what God's word, what this good news brings by way of perspective and insight and salvation to a city brimming with idols submerged in idols.

02:27.180 --> 02:28.802
I'll begin reading in verse 16.

