03:48.780 --> 03:51.184
He's standing in the shadow of the Parthenon.

03:52.387 --> 04:01.522
Does not live in temples made by man, nor is he served by human hands as though he needed anything since he himself gives to all mankind life.

04:01.634 --> 04:03.156
and breath, and everything.

04:03.236 --> 04:22.036
And he, this God, made from one man, every nation of mankind to live on the face of the earth, having determined a lot of periods and the boundaries of their dwelling place, that they should seek God and perhaps feel their way toward him and find him, yet he is actually not far from each one of us.

04:22.417 --> 04:26.321
