24:20.258 --> 24:27.507
Aseity, A-S-E-I-T-Y, Aseity, the God who needs nothing.

24:29.290 --> 24:34.036
So the doctrine of Aseity comes from Latin words meaning from himself.

24:35.057 --> 24:43.187
