27:08.692 --> 27:15.062
Father, glorify me with the glory I had with you before the world existed.

27:15.983 --> 27:31.186
It's an awesome thought to think of this mutual admiration society of love and affirmation within the Godhead for eternity and creation was God inviting us into that joy.

27:31.554 --> 27:35.839
