That's our call.

40:40.048 --> 40:53.249
Incidentally, the reason that our gospel proclamation must be accompanied by the power of the Holy Spirit is precisely because this news doesn't fall naturally and friendly on the ears of a sinful world.

40:53.509 --> 40:56.434
There are offensive elements in the gospel.

40:59.042 --> 41:00.164
So we should expect that.

41:01.606 --> 41:05.632
It's deeply offensive in some way to every culture on the planet.

41:07.215 --> 41:12.263
The gospel message has a confrontational word to every culture on the planet.

41:12.463 --> 41:13.986
Paul said, Jews look for signs.

41:15.087 --> 41:17.171
Greeks seek wisdom, right?

41:17.211 --> 41:18.533
Think about our own context.

41:18.833 --> 41:20.075
Baby boomers want the good life.

41:21.537 --> 41:27.026
Postmoderns want the new tolerance, but we preach Christ and Him crucified.

41:27.874 --> 41:33.911
And this is the power of God and the wisdom of God and the salvation of God of friends.

41:33.971 --> 41:43.858
May we be faithful to preach this and no other gospel, no distorted, no improved gospel, the one we've received from biblical revelation.

